{"ocr_results":[{"text":"(The informant estimates several hundred thousand in all China).'","box":[[185,186],[1313,189],[1313,213],[185,210]]},{"text":"They","box":[[1305,187],[1376,192],[1374,217],[1303,212]]},{"text":"wereattackedforopposingthemovement.","box":[[178,220],[904,222],[903,248],[178,246]]},{"text":"This whole process took about","box":[[897,224],[1392,224],[1392,248],[897,248]]},{"text":"six months.","box":[[181,256],[368,256],[368,280],[181,280]]},{"text":"How did they","box":[[263,287],[476,289],[476,316],[263,314]]},{"text":"decide to investigate people?","box":[[482,289],[985,291],[985,318],[482,316]]},{"text":"Usually oral reports","box":[[1015,294],[1358,294],[1358,318],[1015,318]]},{"text":"from the masses.","box":[[181,323],[476,326],[476,350],[181,347]]},{"text":"People would report something someone had said or done,","box":[[483,323],[1427,324],[1426,355],[483,354]]},{"text":"doubt would grow,than an investigation might start.","box":[[179,356],[1103,362],[1103,388],[179,382]]},{"text":"Members of the East","box":[[1098,361],[1426,360],[1427,384],[1098,385]]},{"text":"Wind faction often reported on Red Flag members.","box":[[177,390],[1035,395],[1035,422],[177,417]]},{"text":"Also units from outside","box":[[1033,395],[1426,394],[1427,418],[1033,419]]},{"text":"would report on people, ask about them (because their relatives also had","box":[[177,425],[1413,426],[1413,456],[177,455]]},{"text":"problems, or someone had made a report on them), or simply the PLA leader","box":[[179,459],[1427,461],[1426,490],[179,488]]},{"text":"would order the special investigation group to investigate someone.","box":[[178,492],[1323,500],[1323,527],[178,519]]},{"text":"The people who had bad class backgrounds (the five black categories)","box":[[264,526],[1423,530],[1422,560],[264,556]]},{"text":"would be put under control of the special investigation group, meaning","box":[[178,561],[1377,566],[1377,596],[178,592]]},{"text":"that they had to report to them every","box":[[182,596],[819,600],[819,627],[182,624]]},{"text":"day.","box":[[828,599],[935,602],[934,627],[828,624]]},{"text":"The others were declared","box":[[929,599],[1342,598],[1342,625],[929,626]]},{"text":"'present day counter-revolutionaries' (","box":[[183,627],[846,630],[846,664],[183,661]]},{"text":"(xianxing fan geming fenzi) if they","box":[[829,633],[1426,634],[1425,662],[829,661]]},{"text":"did not have bad class backgrounds.1","box":[[181,666],[817,668],[817,692],[181,690]]},{"text":"None were sent to labor camps or put","box":[[809,667],[1426,668],[1425,695],[809,694]]},{"text":"in jail at this point.","box":[[181,699],[572,700],[572,727],[181,726]]},{"text":"But they all were put in a cowshed, struggled.","box":[[589,702],[1375,702],[1375,729],[589,729]]},{"text":"Most of them were workers.","box":[[181,736],[661,736],[661,760],[181,760]]},{"text":"Most of them were just released after a couple","box":[[654,735],[1442,735],[1442,762],[654,762]]},{"text":"of months, denied leadership positions, wrote self-examinations, but","box":[[180,768],[1342,769],[1342,796],[180,795]]},{"text":"there was no formal conclusion in their cases.1","box":[[181,801],[1007,803],[1007,830],[181,828]]},{"text":"But allthe materials","box":[[994,805],[1357,805],[1357,828],[994,828]]},{"text":"written down in the course of investigation had to be put in people's","box":[[181,837],[1358,837],[1358,864],[181,864]]},{"text":"files.","box":[[183,873],[302,873],[302,894],[183,894]]},{"text":"This was the principle they worked on, and could not violate it.","box":[[312,870],[1408,871],[1408,898],[312,897]]},{"text":"Only two people","box":[[266,903],[527,906],[527,934],[266,931]]},{"text":"ewere","box":[[515,908],[634,908],[634,929],[515,929]]},{"text":"given formal conclusions to cases.","box":[[622,903],[1205,904],[1205,932],[622,931]]},{"text":"Thry gave them","box":[[1235,904],[1479,904],[1479,934],[1235,934]]},{"text":"a formal paper to sign, said they had uncovered major errors, put the","box":[[178,938],[1361,938],[1361,968],[178,968]]},{"text":"confession in the file.","box":[[181,971],[587,972],[587,999],[181,998]]},{"text":"Most were told that they couldn't find any big","box":[[606,969],[1392,971],[1392,1001],[606,999]]},{"text":"mistakes, only","box":[[181,1008],[421,1008],[421,1032],[181,1032]]},{"text":" small mistakes, so they were told they were being released.","box":[[419,1008],[1440,1008],[1440,1032],[419,1032]]},{"text":"But the third category was the worst, because they didn't come to any","box":[[179,1040],[1359,1040],[1359,1070],[179,1070]]},{"text":"conclusion at all, t","box":[[182,1076],[515,1076],[515,1100],[182,1100]]},{"text":"they just did not come to a conclusion.","box":[[502,1077],[1173,1074],[1174,1101],[502,1104]]},{"text":"But they","box":[[1201,1072],[1342,1076],[1341,1104],[1200,1100]]},{"text":"didn't","box":[[183,1110],[288,1110],[288,1134],[183,1134]]},{"text":" say whether or not the person had a problem.","box":[[275,1112],[1077,1110],[1077,1134],[275,1136]]},{"text":"They just let him go.","box":[[1083,1106],[1443,1109],[1442,1140],[1083,1137]]},{"text":"Basically speaking, those who were attacked in this campaign were","box":[[264,1144],[1380,1142],[1380,1172],[264,1174]]},{"text":"people that the PLA group were dissatisfied with, whose biaoxian in the","box":[[179,1179],[1396,1174],[1396,1204],[179,1209]]},{"text":"CR they were not pleased with.","box":[[184,1215],[729,1215],[729,1239],[184,1239]]},{"text":"Then they went after bad class backgrounds","box":[[725,1212],[1445,1211],[1445,1238],[725,1239]]},{"text":"and other mistakes.","box":[[183,1248],[544,1248],[544,1272],[183,1272]]},{"text":"If the PLA group","box":[[535,1245],[819,1249],[819,1276],[535,1272]]},{"text":"was","box":[[807,1249],[885,1249],[885,1270],[807,1270]]},{"text":"S","box":[[877,1253],[904,1253],[904,1268],[877,1268]]},{"text":"pleased with your biaoxian,","box":[[893,1246],[1356,1247],[1356,1274],[893,1273]]},{"text":"then they would not investigate you.","box":[[183,1281],[795,1282],[795,1309],[183,1308]]},{"text":"This was just part of their work, their main point of concentration","box":[[265,1314],[1413,1314],[1413,1344],[265,1344]]},{"text":"(zhongdianï¼‰.","box":[[185,1348],[420,1350],[420,1378],[185,1376]]},{"text":"Theya","box":[[420,1350],[516,1353],[515,1379],[419,1375]]},{"text":"also had a general investigation (pucha).","box":[[502,1349],[1229,1347],[1229,1374],[502,1376]]},{"text":"All the files","box":[[1236,1347],[1461,1350],[1460,1374],[1236,1371]]},{"text":"on every worker in the plant were gone over by people in the special inves-","box":[[180,1384],[1461,1380],[1461,1410],[180,1414]]},{"text":"tigation group.","box":[[184,1418],[438,1421],[438,1448],[183,1445]]},{"text":"They looked at a)family background, b) personal class","box":[[470,1417],[1377,1415],[1377,1443],[470,1445]]},{"text":"designation, c)political history, d)work history, and e)history of other","box":[[181,1451],[1412,1449],[1412,1479],[181,1481]]},{"text":"family members.","box":[[183,1485],[461,1488],[461,1515],[182,1512]]},{"text":"Theywerelookingtoseeiftherewereanydoubtsabout","box":[[471,1486],[1413,1483],[1413,1509],[471,1512]]},{"text":"the person.","box":[[184,1521],[376,1524],[375,1550],[183,1546]]},{"text":"Were there any gaps","box":[[402,1522],[730,1524],[730,1548],[401,1546]]},{"text":"in the years accounted for in the file?","box":[[778,1518],[1444,1517],[1444,1544],[778,1545]]},{"text":"Before the cleaning of the class ranks campaign was completed, they","box":[[265,1552],[1414,1552],[1414,1582],[265,1582]]},{"text":"had already began the campaign of 'party consolidation and building' (zheng","box":[[180,1585],[1467,1585],[1467,1619],[180,1619]]},{"text":"dang jian dang).","box":[[182,1623],[495,1623],[495,1650],[182,1650]]},{"text":"This new movement meant that attention would be turned","box":[[486,1622],[1415,1619],[1415,1646],[486,1650]]},{"text":"towards party members in the course of these investigations.","box":[[180,1657],[1242,1652],[1242,1682],[180,1687]]},{"text":"They immediately","box":[[1237,1654],[1514,1658],[1514,1685],[1237,1681]]},{"text":"focused on five people, had them halt work and work on self-examinations.","box":[[180,1689],[1430,1688],[1431,1719],[180,1720]]},{"text":"One was a leading cadre who had been criticized in the four cleans movement.","box":[[179,1723],[1482,1722],[1482,1753],[179,1754]]},{"text":"One had said things which were critical of the PLA. At that time it was","box":[[179,1757],[1416,1756],[1416,1787],[179,1788]]},{"text":"illegal to criticize PLA people except to their faces.1","box":[[182,1793],[1148,1790],[1148,1820],[182,1823]]},{"text":"If you said some-","box":[[1132,1791],[1431,1794],[1430,1821],[1132,1818]]},{"text":"thing outside the presence of the PLA, this was called","box":[[182,1827],[1111,1825],[1111,1855],[182,1857]]},{"text":"'spreading rumors'","box":[[1094,1823],[1438,1825],[1437,1856],[1094,1854]]},{"text":"'resisting the PLA',&","box":[[183,1857],[550,1860],[550,1892],[183,1889]]},{"text":"and was against the law, a crime.","box":[[538,1860],[1147,1858],[1147,1885],[538,1887]]},{"text":"Two others had","box":[[1133,1860],[1380,1861],[1380,1885],[1133,1884]]},{"text":"built their own arms for use in armed struggle.(","box":[[181,1895],[1026,1895],[1026,1922],[181,1922]]},{"text":"One was the former head","box":[[1013,1894],[1415,1897],[1414,1921],[1013,1918]]},{"text":"of the security","box":[[181,1931],[443,1932],[443,1956],[181,1955]]},{"text":" department.","box":[[435,1932],[642,1932],[642,1956],[435,1956]]},{"text":"They didn't put these people in a cowshed, they still had the freedom","box":[[265,1963],[1451,1962],[1451,1992],[265,1993]]},{"text":"to leave the plant.","box":[[183,2001],[546,2001],[546,2025],[183,2025]]},{"text":" But a lot of the workers wanted the old security","box":[[533,1994],[1365,1998],[1365,2029],[533,2025]]},{"text":"department head put in a cell, because he had suppressed","box":[[180,2033],[1147,2030],[1147,2060],[180,2063]]},{"text":"1 workers so much","box":[[1132,2035],[1416,2036],[1416,2060],[1132,2059]]},{"text":"before the CR.","box":[[181,2071],[423,2071],[423,2095],[181,2095]]},{"text":"They put up a lot of wallposters at this time demanding this.","box":[[452,2068],[1501,2068],[1501,2098],[452,2098]]},{"text":"-15-","box":[[851,2119],[916,2119],[916,2145],[851,2145]]}],"dimensions":{"height":2210,"width":1562}}